  "text": [
    "The snail at the edge of the road",
    "inches forward, a trim gray finger",
    "of a fellow in pinstripe suit.",
    "He\u2019s burdened by his house",
    "that has to follow",
    "where he goes. Every inch,",
    "he pulls together",
    "all he is,",
    "all he owns,",
    "all he was given.",
    "The road is wide",
    "but he is called",
    "by something",
    "that knows him",
    "on the other side."
  ],
  "title": "The Crossing",
  "year": ""
